            {
                "s2_paper_id": "fa412338c6f27c3c88de8b6bdac48daca776b198",
                "title": "Maintaining an Active Organic Class during the COVID-Induced Online Transition at Two Undergraduate Institutions",
                "year": 2020,
                "venue": "",
                "citation_count": 9,
                "reference_count": 22,
                "abstract": "This communication contains the experience of two early-career organic professors at primarily undergraduate institutions during the rapid transition to an online learning environment during the COVID-19 pandemic. The techniques and methods for transitioning both the organic lecture and lab of two class sizes (\u223c50 and \u223c10) are juxtaposed, and conclusions are drawn that provide insight into improvements for both online and on-site learning.",
